d - despite the blazing heat - roaring as their man crossed the line for his blistering championship finish.\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1779, \"end\": 1795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Proud\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1693}, {\"ngram\": \"Enhanced Games Sports quiz\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1726}, {\"ngram\": \"100 hard questions\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible year\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand Slam Track decision\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1827}, {\"ngram\": \"2025 ambitions\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1846}, {\"ngram\": \"trips\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"autumn\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1887}, {\"ngram\": \"winter\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"the hosts\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"the blazing heat - roaring\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"their man\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2030}, {\"ngram\": \"his blistering championship finish\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Burgess finished fourth-fastest from the afternoon's semis in 97.21 seconds, a penalty-free run that nevertheless highlighted a few areas of improvement as he navigated a tricky middle section, keeping calm to assure himself a chance at a medal.\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Burgess\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"the afternoon's semis\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2134}, {\"ngram\": \"97.21 seconds\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"